{"title":"春天的歌","authors":["叶晓山","尹安贵","车美萍"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":4,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春曲二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶晓山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春播"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老农弯腰忙春播，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手撒出万支歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万支歌——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞进田间长绿禾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进秋场涌金波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜风细雨听无声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杏花渡口桨儿轻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桨儿轻——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裁得两岸似画屏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪出一幅江南春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山城春雾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尹安贵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜的梦有清泉有暖风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只天鹅飘然飞来山城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来果然看见她洁白的羽毛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双柔软的翅膀漫天垂下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻覆盖着初生的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她独立在高楼的阳台上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衔着一枚红红的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是她那温柔的翅膀一收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融融的阳光滴落无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个明丽的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘飘洒洒在人间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明的溪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车美萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当紫燕从远方衔来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸柳丝的嫩绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小船——我曾经冻僵的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢跃了，与出浴的鸭群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流一河透明的韵律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时我很温顺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如羞涩一笑的渔家少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮大妈搓洗冬衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗去被浓雾染上的忧郁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时又很调皮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱与泥鳅一样的儿童们嬉戏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起浪花的巴掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍打他们腿肚子上的污泥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深山给我一颗晶莹的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的倒影才珍藏心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为涤荡污浊而奔腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕迂回也充满希冀……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}